57
00:01:43,770 --> 00:01:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We can overcome anything</i></font>

58
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>tatakitsukero Emotion</i></font>

59
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Drum to your emotion</i></font>

60
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're both fast asleep.</font>

61
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were pretty drained.
We'll leave after they're rested.</font>

62
00:02:22,140 --> 00:02:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something wrong, Cougarmon?</font>

63
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

64
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must have been my imagination.</font>

65
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">DEFIANCE</font>

66
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Curse you, Kanada.</i></font>

67
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Placing a bounty on Sir Klay.</font>

68
00:02:52,170 --> 00:02:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Relax.</i></font>

69
00:02:54,130 --> 00:02:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gather all Tactics forces.</i></font>

70
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think Chairman Wong...</font>

71
00:03:01,010 --> 00:03:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">needs to be removed.</font>

72
00:03:06,730 --> 00:03:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still have unfinished business.
If you'll excuse me.</i></font>

73
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

74
00:03:12,070 --> 00:03:14,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I promise you that I will return in time.</i></font>

75
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:18,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As you wish, Sir Klay,
everything will be perfect.</i></font>

76
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do as you will.</font>

77
00:03:21,450 --> 00:03:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you intend to do?</font>

78
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyo Sawashiro of the Glowing Dawn.</font>

79
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the only "perfect"
that Sir Klay needs.</font>

80
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kanuma, find the traitor Granit
and eliminate him.</font>

81
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

82
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rules of the Tactics. Rule!</font>

83
00:03:41,720 --> 00:03:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None shall disobey an order.</font>

84
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we lose here, your path to being
a researcher will be gone for good.</font>

85
00:03:51,820 --> 00:03:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So much for supporting your family.</font>

86
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:57,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roger.</font>

87
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure?</font>

88
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do it.</font>

89
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

90
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hotaruko?</font>

91
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What... are you doing?</font>

92
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?!</font>

93
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

94
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's taking so long, Kanuma?</font>

95
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were my orders too difficult for you?</font>

96
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Sir.</font>

97
00:04:58,260 --> 00:04:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want?</font>

98
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my target, Kyo Sawashiro.</font>

99
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do it!</font>

100
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cougarmon!</font>

101
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evolve!</font>

102
00:05:22,910 --> 00:05:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cougarmon Evolution!</font>

103
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Murasamemon!</font>

104
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh my. You actually blocked it.</font>

105
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad at all, Mr. Naito.</font>

106
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's that?!</font>

107
00:05:58,610 --> 00:05:59,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Five Star!</font>

108
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Five Star, Star of Water.
Honoka the Abyssal!</font>

109
00:06:03,700 --> 00:06:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On orders from Chairman Wong,
the bounty Klay Arslan and the Tactics...</font>

110
00:06:10,540 --> 00:06:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are my prey!</font>

111
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Klay Arslan is a bounty?</font>

112
00:06:15,540 --> 00:06:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, a Five Star...</font>

113
00:06:18,130 --> 00:06:19,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never met her.</font>

114
00:06:20,130 --> 00:06:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

115
00:06:21,590 --> 00:06:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she's telling the truth.</font>

116
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know about you.
You're Kyo Sawashiro, right?</font>

117
00:06:28,350 --> 00:06:30,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem pretty boring.</font>

118
00:06:30,890 --> 00:06:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does Kaito-sama see in you?</font>

119
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh well. Right now
it's Tactics clean-up time!</font>

120
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gigasmon!</font>

121
00:06:47,780 --> 00:06:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kanuma.</font>

122
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the very least, act as a shield.
Take her out, or die trying!</font>

123
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said I'm your target.</font>

124
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want?</font>

125
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:19,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll eliminate you.</font>

126
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't have you interfere
with Sir Klay any further!</font>

127
00:07:23,650 --> 00:07:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurricane Bomber!</font>

128
00:07:25,860 --> 00:07:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Murasamemon!</font>

129
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jyunozan Tsukishigure!</font>

130
00:07:48,970 --> 00:07:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Earthquake!</font>

131
00:08:01,150 --> 00:08:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Torpedo Attack!</font>

132
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makocchan!</font>

133
00:08:10,990 --> 00:08:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll take Granit and the others!
We're counting on you!</font>

134
00:08:14,450 --> 00:08:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

135
00:08:15,330 --> 00:08:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tomoro, can you walk?</font>

136
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chiropmon!</font>

137
00:08:20,330 --> 00:08:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here goes!</font>

138
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fly!</font>

139
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:41,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chiropmon Evolution!</font>

140
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nightchiropmon!</font>

141
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Providence Scan!</font>

142
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shadow Arts!</font>

143
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

144
00:09:07,710 --> 00:09:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aqua Viper!</font>

145
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Giant Rang!</font>

146
00:09:16,850 --> 00:09:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't your fight!</font>

147
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're an Ultimate Digimon!</font>

148
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hotaruko! We have to work together!</font>

149
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:26,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need help!</font>

150
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no escape!</font>

151
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

152
00:09:58,060 --> 00:10:01,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Using cheap tricks
because you can't win fairly?</font>

153
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such a boring way to fight.</font>

154
00:10:03,850 --> 00:10:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Textbook strategy of a goody-two-shoes.</font>

155
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:14,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops. Too bad.</font>

156
00:10:19,540 --> 00:10:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nightchiropmon!</font>

157
00:10:35,090 --> 00:10:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

158
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never stopped running.</i></font>

159
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:47,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My family was poor.</i></font>

160
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It led to constant ridicule.</i></font>

161
00:10:50,230 --> 00:10:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I studied as hard as I could
to get them to shut up.</i></font>

162
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hotaruko.</font>

163
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on your internship.</font>

164
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're finally a researcher.
I'm so proud of you.</font>

165
00:11:02,700 --> 00:11:04,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is nothing, Mother.</font>

166
00:11:05,420 --> 00:11:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to send money, you know.</font>

167
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The store's getting by
thanks to our regulars.</font>

168
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I want is for you to be happy.</font>

169
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

170
00:11:20,850 --> 00:11:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted to ease Mother's burden.
I just wanted to be independent.</i></font>

171
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can do this. I'm fine on my own.</i></font>

172
00:11:29,810 --> 00:11:32,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I desperately told myself that.</i></font>

173
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Miss Kanuma, we can take over.
You should get some rest.</i></font>

174
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been cooped up in here.</font>

175
00:11:40,910 --> 00:11:42,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm fine.</i></font>

176
00:11:42,290 --> 00:11:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I need is today's test data
and I'll be good.</i></font>

177
00:11:48,370 --> 00:11:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And then... one day...</i></font>

178
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your e-Pulse readings are abnormal.</i></font>

179
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please ensure adequate sleep.</i></font>

180
00:11:58,010 --> 00:11:59,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh be quiet.</font>

181
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Error! Error! Error! Error!</i></font>

182
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-What?</font>

183
00:12:22,830 --> 00:12:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shakomon was born.</i></font>

184
00:12:25,950 --> 00:12:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I couldn't remain in college.</i></font>

185
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ever since the Klay Foundation
took on my debts, my life has been chaos.</i></font>

186
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I can repay my debts and get results,
I can be a researcher again.</i></font>

187
00:12:41,050 --> 00:12:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have time to stop.</i></font>

188
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:47,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hotaruko...</font>

189
00:12:48,350 --> 00:12:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can endure any ocean,
no matter how dark or cold.</font>

190
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:56,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Makoto Kuonji.</i></font>

191
00:12:57,190 --> 00:13:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Unable to make hard decisions.
Always dependent on your friends.</i></font>

192
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm made of stronger stuff
than a spoiled kid like you.</i></font>

193
00:13:07,410 --> 00:13:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can be strong on my own!</i></font>

194
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's what I always believed, but...</i></font>

195
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh come on. This is boring!</font>

196
00:13:31,730 --> 00:13:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so weak it's pathetic.
Shall I just end it for you?</font>

197
00:13:35,940 --> 00:13:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that okay?</font>

198
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:40,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure it is, isn't it?</font>

199
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill.</font>

200
00:13:59,710 --> 00:14:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hotaruko, are you okay?</font>

201
00:14:06,970 --> 00:14:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you stand? Let's go!</font>

202
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't.</font>

203
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't win. I can't escape.</font>

204
00:14:18,690 --> 00:14:19,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just...</font>

205
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">leave me.</font>

206
00:14:22,570 --> 00:14:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hotaruko...</font>

207
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why should I?</font>

208
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:32,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if we can't win individually,
maybe we can win together!</font>

209
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have your family!
You have your Tactics friends!</font>

210
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have Shakomon!</font>

211
00:14:40,210 --> 00:14:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with helping each other?</font>

212
00:14:43,930 --> 00:14:47,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! There you are!</font>

213
00:14:47,350 --> 00:14:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Tactics aren't some big,
happy family like you guys!</font>

214
00:14:53,310 --> 00:14:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They never help...</font>

215
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take them out!</font>

216
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tialudomon!</font>

217
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

218
00:15:18,330 --> 00:15:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They ain't alone, ya know!</font>

219
00:15:20,210 --> 00:15:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here, too!</font>

220
00:15:22,050 --> 00:15:23,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makocchan!</font>

221
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:24,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

222
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:26,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reina! Tomoro!</font>

223
00:15:27,010 --> 00:15:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Granit...</font>

224
00:15:31,010 --> 00:15:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

225
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I tried to...</font>

226
00:15:35,890 --> 00:15:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know either.</font>

227
00:15:38,270 --> 00:15:39,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

228
00:15:39,810 --> 00:15:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think I'll sleep well if you die.</font>

229
00:15:44,030 --> 00:15:46,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just say you want to protect your friend.</font>

230
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hotaruko, you're not alone.</font>

231
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't like you.</font>

232
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... if Makoto wants to protect you,
I'll help.</font>

233
00:15:58,460 --> 00:16:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to make up your mind!</font>

234
00:16:00,670 --> 00:16:02,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll fight together with you!</font>

235
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:05,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, please trust us!</font>

236
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:13,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait! Stop it!</font>

237
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm allergic to cheap melodrama!</font>

238
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't stand weaklings standing up
for each other! Gross! I'm getting chills!</font>

239
00:16:29,110 --> 00:16:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm bored. Bye.</font>

240
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Hey!</font>

241
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get you for this.</font>

242
00:16:36,450 --> 00:16:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck?</font>

243
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think she let us go?</font>

244
00:16:41,580 --> 00:16:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget her! We need to help Kyo!</font>

245
00:16:45,340 --> 00:16:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't speak up
out of respect for your wishes, but...</font>

246
00:16:50,380 --> 00:16:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">rather than enduring
the dark and cold...</font>

247
00:16:53,510 --> 00:16:58,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think swimming in the open sea
suits you better.</font>

248
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shakomon...</font>

249
00:17:01,060 --> 00:17:04,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what you choose,
I'll always be with you.</font>

250
00:17:06,570 --> 00:17:07,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

251
00:17:11,610 --> 00:17:14,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Let's go!</font>

252
00:17:20,250 --> 00:17:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hunt them all down!</font>

253
00:17:27,130 --> 00:17:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shakomon Evolution!</font>

254
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tylomon!</font>

255
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gounozan Murashigure!</font>

256
00:17:47,730 --> 00:17:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?!
Defeat is not an option for the Tactics!</font>

257
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sand doppelgangers?</font>

258
00:18:10,210 --> 00:18:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Murasamemon!</font>

259
00:18:15,090 --> 00:18:17,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's over!</font>

260
00:18:21,430 --> 00:18:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Torpedo Attack!</font>

261
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

262
00:18:28,650 --> 00:18:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyo!</font>

263
00:18:31,280 --> 00:18:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kanuma. Granit.</font>

264
00:18:34,070 --> 00:18:37,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So both of you are betraying the Tactics?</font>

265
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ungrateful brat!
Have you forgotten your promise?</font>

266
00:18:43,410 --> 00:18:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about your family's...</font>

267
00:18:48,090 --> 00:18:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll protect my family no matter what.</font>

268
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll repay my own debts.</font>

269
00:18:54,180 --> 00:18:58,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Team Seven will never
follow your orders again.</font>

270
00:18:59,430 --> 00:19:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hereby tender my resignation.</font>

271
00:19:01,850 --> 00:19:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you...</font>

272
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:08,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get lost, you piece of filth.</font>

273
00:19:11,570 --> 00:19:15,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not much of a leader
if your team is betraying you.</font>

274
00:19:17,410 --> 00:19:19,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am true perfection.</font>

275
00:19:19,740 --> 00:19:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the one worthy of Sir Klay!</font>

276
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll erase all of you
from my perfect world!</font>

277
00:19:36,130 --> 00:19:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That thing's bad news, ya know!</font>

278
00:19:38,220 --> 00:19:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to run!</font>

279
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:41,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No we don't.</font>

280
00:19:41,970 --> 00:19:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You tried to hurt my family.</font>

281
00:19:45,180 --> 00:19:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to pay!</font>

282
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsuinozan Kokuu!</font>

283
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible.</font>

284
00:20:27,390 --> 00:20:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're fleeing?!</font>

285
00:20:28,850 --> 00:20:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

286
00:20:29,980 --> 00:20:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you use the monkey Digimon
to lure me to the colosseum?</font>

287
00:20:35,780 --> 00:20:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll eliminate that Digimon!</font>

288
00:20:39,110 --> 00:20:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's none of your concern!</font>

289
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh dear. Back to the drawing board.</font>

290
00:20:54,340 --> 00:20:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be fine. We're capable.</font>

291
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:01,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you two do?</font>

292
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll look for Raito.</font>

293
00:21:03,890 --> 00:21:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll return to the Mirror World.</font>

294
00:21:05,930 --> 00:21:08,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a fellow Tactics member after all.</font>

295
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look after him.</font>

296
00:21:14,150 --> 00:21:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for everything.</font>

297
00:21:24,660 --> 00:21:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job!</font>

298
00:21:25,990 --> 00:21:27,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this about?</font>

299
00:21:27,830 --> 00:21:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just glad you're all okay.</font>

300
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get some expensive meat today.</font>

301
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meat!</font>

302
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:36,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't! We're still cutting back!</font>

303
00:21:36,500 --> 00:21:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let go already! You're suffocating me!</font>

304
00:21:39,470 --> 00:21:41,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm hungry, ya know!</font>

305
00:21:45,510 --> 00:21:46,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chairman Wong.</font>

306
00:21:47,350 --> 00:21:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Tactics have been
almost completely wiped out.</font>

307
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>atarimae wo atarimae ni shinai</i></font>

308
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't let the normal be normal</i></font>

309
00:22:05,870 --> 00:22:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>gakufu doori ja monotarinaindayo</i></font>

310
00:22:05,870 --> 00:22:08,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Playing to the score is not enough</i></font>

311
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>noizu sura mo torikonde
jibun dake no sesshon wo!</i></font>

312
00:22:08,620 --> 00:22:13,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Take in everything, even the noise
And make it our own session!</i></font>

313
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>hitomakase ja kawaranaishi
Boot! Boot!</i></font>

314
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Things won't change in others' hands
Boot! Boot!</i></font>

315
00:22:17,340 --> 00:22:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>te nobase</i></font>

316
00:22:17,340 --> 00:22:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Reach out your hand</i></font>

317
00:22:18,550 --> 00:22:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>machigai mo osorezu susume
Boot! Boot!</i></font>

318
00:22:18,550 --> 00:22:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't be scared to mess up, go on
Boot! Boot!</i></font>

319
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>yuukan ni</i></font>

320
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With courage</i></font>

321
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>ruuru ni tatakitsukeru NO
error, error</i></font>

322
00:22:23,550 --> 00:22:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Go tell the rules NO
Error, error</i></font>

323
00:22:26,390 --> 00:22:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>sukeeru auto joutou
error, error</i></font>

324
00:22:26,390 --> 00:22:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Scale out? Bring it on
Error, error</i></font>

325
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>yosoku funou no koodo
error, error</i></font>

326
00:22:28,760 --> 00:22:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An unexpected code
Error, error</i></font>

327
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>puronpto nanka ja seigyoudekinai omoide</i></font>

328
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prompts can't control these feelings</i></font>

329
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>kamase shauto</i></font>

330
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Give it a shout</i></font>

331
00:22:37,570 --> 00:22:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>BRAVE! mou kowakunai</i></font>

332
00:22:37,570 --> 00:22:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>BRAVE! No more fear</i></font>

333
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>utsumuitari mo shinai</i></font>

334
00:22:40,030 --> 00:22:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Keep my head high</i></font>

335
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>senaka azukeaeru kimi ga iru kara</i></font>

336
00:22:42,360 --> 00:22:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've got someone who's got my back</i></font>

337
00:22:47,490 --> 00:22:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>GROOVE! mou tomaranai</i></font>

338
00:22:47,490 --> 00:22:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>GROOVE! We can't be stopped</i></font>

339
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>yunizon suru koudou ga</i></font>

340
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:52,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our beats are in unison</i></font>

341
00:22:52,450 --> 00:22:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>kitto sekaijuu wo appudeeto shiteiku</i></font>

342
00:22:52,450 --> 00:22:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're going to update the world</i></font>

343
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<i>bakuon de</i></font>

344
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With a bang</i></font>

345
00:23:03,380 --> 00:23:05,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's go, Kyo!</i></font>

346
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We're counting on you!</i></font>

347
00:23:07,180 --> 00:23:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're gonna make a world where
